creator: Real Consulting Data
descriptionHtml:
An open data healthcare tool made to accompany physicians & patients on their rare disease journey and reducing diagnostic errancy by using the latest data and technology.

Use the screening tool to guide you. Search for rare diseases, phenotypes, genes and expert centers and access detailed descriptions. We combine reliable sources such as Orphanet, HPO, the French Ministry of Health, etc.
